Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.33,0:02:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神來做早操吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，先從腕部運動開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不用做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，早安ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，吵醒你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.27,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在大掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在曬榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大掃除啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.11,0:02:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.98,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#17         ちぃ，幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們經常受您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.63,0:03:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公寓裡大掃除的工作\N不也需要男人幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話\N請盡量派工作給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，發現灰塵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現灰塵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡，就是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這裡也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣做，知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，那來掃除吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，要掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接下來要擦外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ留在這裡看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拉一下，再拉一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拉一下，再拉一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拉一下，再拉一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，啪啪啪啪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻，嘿咻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.94,0:05:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣嗎？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我陷入危機了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輩子最大的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…\N我找到適合ちぃ的衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓她穿穿看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以，謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.16,0:08:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，ちぃ\N妳能到我房裡來一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別給日比谷小姐添麻煩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來把搬出去的東西\N歸位就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得二樓樓上好像也有窗戶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.69,0:09:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能穿穿看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是通往屋頂的門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這是倉庫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.00,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我換好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然很合身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這原本就是妳的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的衣服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳全都忘了，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ忘了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是那個人的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.73,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這麼多電線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之把灰塵清一清吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會跑出什麼怪東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲…絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.61,0:11:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒…醒醒啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被新保知道\N絲茉茉壞掉了的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉\N絲茉茉好像壞掉了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是道歉就能了事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我賠一台來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉觸電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話\N就讓我倒杯麥茶給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了\N出問題時要跟稔聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，請問是國分寺宅嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓本須和\N請問稔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？出門了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在這時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還好，但絲茉茉就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.31,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳穿那是什麼德性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿這樣不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有什麼不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是很喜歡妳穿這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.96,0:13:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是管理員小姐給妳的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是管理員小姐交給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是“管理員小姐給妳的”就好了\Nちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“給”是在“接受”時用的詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.67,0:13:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是ちぃ的東西\N所以不是“接受”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打給新保嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也只有絲茉茉才知道號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.56,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，醒醒啊，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的話\N要不要讓我來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.56,0:13:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是指絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍微看看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.69,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N看來突波防護裝置有正常運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？突波？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.57,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她裝有避免檔案\N被突發電流破壞的裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.37,0:14:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以資料並沒有受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.28,0:14:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是被電流給電暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也提起精神來做早操吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間好像有點錯亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來修正一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不太懂這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一開始都是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我保管期間內壞掉的話\N可不是開玩笑的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.66,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好像去旅行還是幹嘛去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要長期保管的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,設定一下\N使用者密碼比較好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.04,0:15:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這樣就能避免\N絲茉茉遭到他人使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.98,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在設定成誰都可以使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.21,0:15:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣一來\N就不能保護個人資料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐妳很懂電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.92,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從事過電腦相關的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳打字才這麼快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在妳已經不做了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N所以才來這裡當管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，只是覺得有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.34,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間公寓原本是屬於我先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，是妳丈夫的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐妳結婚啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.85,0:16:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.82,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先生跟我都是從事電腦業的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐已經結婚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我先生過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.36,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就決定\N自己來守護著這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是他的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.11,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和\N今晚請到我那裡吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要謝謝你\N今天幫我掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.46,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，盡是些常見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是畫中才有的家庭式料理嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.64,0:17:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，ちぃ最近比較常笑了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是…是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.48,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是因為\N本須和很重視ちぃ的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ真的越來越可愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.77,0:18:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會讓他們更容易找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了不少事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也吃了不少好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷小姐好像提到了\N密碼之類的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要設定密碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在公用模式下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果設定使用者登錄的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.71,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能阻郲他人使用絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要設定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就請輸入密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼用“本須和”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個密碼不受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姓名、生日、電話等\N容易被他人獲知的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不建議用來當作密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用生日、電話以外的密碼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.96,0:19:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,語音確認\N語音確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要使用平假名還是片假名呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不建議使用同一類型  的文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.11,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建議將平假、片假\N英文字母與數字混合使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼將第一個“CH”用平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼設定完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.93,0:20:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不知道有沒有密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的，就是她的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.99,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還蠻近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們果然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.01,0:22:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.98,0:22:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.09,0:22:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.27,0:23:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.86,0:23:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.29,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.33,0:23:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛 也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.08,0:23:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠 直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦為什麼要做成人的模樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都辦得到，方便，又美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直陪伴在人的身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.97,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過又與真人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.37,0:23:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.58,0:23:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來煩惱就夠多的重考生\N怎麼能再增加煩惱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.55,0:24:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits  下一回\N「ちぃ，不見了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.45,0:24:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.95,0:24:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也是電腦吧
